25 July 2008President Thabo Mbeki will address the media this Sunday, on the outcomes of the Cabinet Lekgotla which took place from 22 to 24 July 2008 at the Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria.Details of the briefing are as follows:Date: 27 July 2008 (Sunday) Venue: Media Centre, Room 153, Union Buildings, Pretoria Time: 14:00Note: There will be a video-link to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Media are requested to confirm their attendance with:Matshepo Seedat Email: matshepo@gcis.gov.za Cell: 083 228 5041Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Mukoni Ratshitanga (Cape Town) Cell: 082 300 3447Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)